@ControlPlane.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5109

### Get all agents
GET {{ControlPlane.Api_HostAddress}}/v1/agents
Accept: application/json

###

### Create an agent
POST {{ControlPlane.Api_HostAddress}}/v1/agents
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Invoice Classifier",
  "instructions": "Classify invoices by vendor and route appropriately",
  "modelProfile": {
    "model": "gpt-4",
    "temperature": 0.7
  }
}

###

### Get all nodes
GET {{ControlPlane.Api_HostAddress}}/v1/nodes
Accept: application/json

###

### Register a node
POST {{ControlPlane.Api_HostAddress}}/v1/nodes:register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nodeId": "node-1",
  "metadata": {
    "region": "us-east-1",
    "environment": "dev"
  },
  "capacity": {
    "slots": 8,
    "cpu": "4",
    "memory": "8Gi"
  }
}

###

### Get all runs
GET {{ControlPlane.Api_HostAddress}}/v1/runs
Accept: application/json

###
